  <div class="container">
    <p class="kicker reveal">Integrations</p>
    <h2 class="reveal">Where Technology Meets Human-Centric Recruiting</h2>
    <p class="lead reveal">
      TalentOS connects our recruiting teams, your hiring managers, and your existing HR technology stack into a single operating system. We use AI to accelerate sourcing, screening, and calibration—while keeping every interaction human, personal, and aligned to your culture.
    </p>
    <p class="lead reveal" style="margin-top: 16px;">
      TalentOS integrates with leading ATS, HRIS, payroll, collaboration, background check, and global employment platforms including Greenhouse, BambooHR, ADP, Slack, LinkedIn, Google, Candidately, Accurate, Bullhorn, and Deel.
    </p>
    <p class="lead reveal" style="margin-top: 16px; font-size: 14px; color: var(--text-muted);">
